- Patch Selector: two tabs added ("Banks" and "Tags") to switch between two preset listing modes;
- now you can tap Next and Previous patch button without closing Patch Selector;
- scrolling the list of presets in the Patch Selector now works faster;
- Share preset function added (in Settings->Utilities) to share preset or bank without having to save it to the Files;
- now you are allowed to save (export) or share a single preset that you need (not just a full bank);
- swipe left in the "Load User Bank" file list dialog to manually delete unnecessary bank files from Poison's Documents folder (no need to use Files.app);
- in the FX selector, you can now select an effect for editing by simply tapping on a corresponding led, instead of using Select button.

And a special addition:

- introducing new factory Bank F with 100 incredible experimental patches, created by sks2002, which were used for his tracks! The presets were also processed and mastered by Jim Pavloff;
- 8 new factory presets added to Bank E: E86-E93, be sure to check them out!
- some of the original factory presets were modified to sound better (A23, A25, A72, A73, A92, A96, E41, E45 and E84).

- fixed AUv3 crash upon load in some audio host apps;
- in Scale play mode, root notes on the keyboard are now marked with red color for your comfort;
- now you can examine current parameter values just by tapping desired knob or fader;
- Audiobus SDK updated to v3.0.12;
- minor bug fixes and iOS 14 support.

In this update:
- a quick fix for iPhone 12 Pro Max display resolution support.

In previous 2.5.2 update:
- fixed AUv3 crash upon load in some audio host apps;
- in Scale play mode, root notes on the keyboard are now marked with red color for your comfort;
- now you can examine current parameter values just by tapping desired knob or fader;
- Audiobus SDK updated to v3.0.12;
- minor bug fixes and iOS 14 support.
